Tibiyo Taka Ngwane, nke pụtara akụ na ụba nke mba ahụ, bụ ego akụ na ụba Swazi nke e mepụtara site na eze Eze Mswati nke Atọ na-ejide ụlọ ọrụ ahụ ugbu a na ntụkwasị obi maka mba Swazi ma dị iche na gọọmentị.

Eze Sobhuza nke Abụọ hibere ya na nnwere onwe na 1968 site n'aka Royal Charter iji kwalite na ịkwado udo na nkwụsi ike, ichekwa omenala na ọdịnala na ịkwalite ọkwa obibi ndụ dị elu maka mba Swazi site n'inye ọrụ

O nwere oke n'ọrụ ugbo, ihe onwunwe, ụlọ ọrụ na-ebi akwụkwọ, ma ọ bụ naanị ya nwe Eswatini Observer. Tibiyo bụ onye nwere òkè n'ọtụtụ ụlọ ọrụ dịka Royal Eswatini Sugar Corporation (RES Corporation), Maloma Colliery Limited, Lubombo Sugar, Parmalat Swaziland, Simunye Plaza, Bhuna Mall, Swazi Spar Holdings, Eswatini Beverages, Alexander Forbes, Fincorp, Tibiyo Leisure Resorts na-azụ ahịa dị ka Royal Villas na ọtụtụ ndị enyemaka gafee mba ahụ.
N'afọ 2009, otu ìgwè ndị Swazi kpọrọ oku ka a gbanwee Tibiyo Taka Ngwane ka ọ bụrụ ngalaba gọọmentị nke ga-emeghe maka nyocha ọha na eze.
